  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe send button is being hidden as expected, however the drag and drop functionality still works, so it looks like the user can send images to a public chat. in reality it doens't seem the messages are actually sent.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. join a public channel\r\n2. drag an image from your file explorer into the text input\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nthe drag and drop behaviour should be disabled and not even show. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nthe image is attached to the message and can be sent, and display in the chat log. in practice though the meesage is not actually sent\r\n\r\n",
